videos.headline: Herbert connects with Breeland for Oregon TD
videos.description: Justin Herbert rolls out of the pocket and finds Jacob Breeland for a seven-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Redd hauls in 13-yard TD

videos.headline: McKinley stays in for INT
videos.description: Steven Montez lofts a pass to the end zone that is tipped up in the air and Verone McKinley III flies in for the pick.
